      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LIGHTNING QUICK (1) has an excellent record over this journey having never missed the placings in four starts, including two wins and two placings. Scored by 11 lengths last time (41.72) in a Grade 5 over 715m at this track. Looks well placed and should feature. LAKEVIEW HUNTER (5) is progressing well scoring last time out (42.12) at this track and bringing up his 9th career win. Has a good record at this journey. Winner at his latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. Bold showing expected again. CHARLESTOWN (7) missed the frame last time when fourth (34.60) at this track but prior to that had two placings in a row. Has a good record at this journey. Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Cannot be underestimated. MEPUNGA BREEZE (2) placed last time (42.24) at this track in a Grade 4/5, finishing third and beaten 1.75 lengths. Has two wins already from this draw.",
